# The static QuickNotes binary `quicknotes` is shipped here.
# Build it (from the repo root) before running the playbook:
#
#   CGO_ENABLED=0 go build -C app -o ../ansible/files/quicknotes .
#
# CGO_ENABLED=0 makes a fully static binary so it runs on the VM with no libc
# version coupling. The binary itself is a build artifact and is not committed.
